Description

Administrative body of the capital city of Stockholm.

The Municipality of Stockholm (Cemeteries Administration) represents the Skogskyrkogården and the Northern Cemetery of Stockholm (Norra begravningsplatsen) in the European Cemeteries Route, Cultural Route of the Council of Europe.
